wn menu'=>'drop-down menu','Questions and answers'=>'Questions and answers','Quiz'=>'Quiz','quiz'=>'quiz','Sender does not enter the correct answer to the quiz'=>'Sender does not enter the correct answer to the quiz','Slider'=>'Slider','Spinbox'=>'Spinbox','Number field'=>'Number field','number'=>'number','Number is larger than maximum limit'=>'Number is larger than the maximum limit','Number is smaller than minimum limit'=>'Number is smaller than the minimum limit','Number format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'Number format that the sender entered is invalid','This contact form has file uploading fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'This contact form has file uploading fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.','Acceptable file types'=>'Acceptable file types','file'=>'file','Uploading a file fails for PHP error'=>'Uploading a file fails due to a PHP error','Uploaded file is too large'=>'Uploaded file is too large','Uploaded file is not allowed for file type'=>'Uploaded file is not allowed for this file type','Uploading a file fails for any reason'=>'Uploading a file fails for any reason','Max'=>'Max','Min'=>'Min','Range'=>'Range','Default value'=>'Default value','Date field'=>'Date field','date'=>'date','Date is later than maximum limit'=>'Date is later than the maximum limit','Date is earlier than minimum limit'=>'Date is earlier than the minimum limit','Date format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'The date format that the sender entered is invalid','Wrap each item with a label element.'=>'Wrap each item with a label element.','Field type'=>'Field type','radio buttons'=>'radio buttons','checkboxes'=>'checkboxes','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the necessary libraries (GD and FreeType) are not available on your server.'=>'This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the necessary libraries (GD and FreeType) are not available on your server.','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.','Your entered code is incorrect.'=>'Your entered code is incorrect.','The code that sender entered does not match the CAPTCHA'=>'The code that the sender entered does not match the CAPTCHA','Insert Tag'=>'Insert Tag','Class attribute'=>'Class attribute','ID attribute'=>'ID attribute','Acceptance checkbox'=>'Acceptance checkbox','acceptance'=>'acceptance','<code>%1$s</code> property of a <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> object is <strong>no longer accessible</strong>. Use <code>%2$s</code> method instead.'=>'<code>%1$s</code> property of a <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> object is <strong>no longer accessible</strong>. Use <code>%2$s</code> method instead.','Untitled'=>'Untitled','Contact Form'=>'Contact Form','There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length'=>'There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length','There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length'=>'There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length','There is a field that the sender must fill in'=>'There is a field that the sender must fill in','There are terms that the sender must accept'=>'There are terms that the sender must accept','Submission was referred to as spam'=>'Submission was referred to as spam','Validation errors occurred'=>'Validation errors occurred','Sender&#8217;s message was sent successfully'=>'Sender&#8217;s message was sent successfully','Message Body:'=>'Message Body:','Subject: %s'=>'Subject: %s','From: %s'=>'From: %s','Send'=>'Send','Your message'=>'Your message','Your email'=>'Your email','Your name'=>'Your name','Form-tag Generator: %s'=>'Form-tag Generator: %s','For more information:'=>'For more information:','Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorization.'=>'Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorisation.','You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorize Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account.'=>'You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorise Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account.','On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available.'=>'On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using the API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available.','There are also special mail-tags that have specific names, but do not have corresponding form-tags. They are used to represent meta information of form submissions like the submitter&#8217;s IP address or the URL of the page.'=>'There are also special mail-tags that have specific names, but do not have corresponding form-tags. They are used to represent meta information of form submissions like the submitter&#8217;s IP address or the URL of the page.','A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag.'=>'A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag.','While form-tags have a comparatively complex syntax, you do not need to know the syntax to add form-tags because you can use the straightforward tag generator (<strong>Generate Tag</strong> button on this screen).'=>'While form-tags have a comparatively complex syntax, you do not need to know the syntax to add form-tags because you can use the straightforward tag generator (<strong>Generate Tag</strong> button on this screen).','A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields.'=>'A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields.','<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customize the behavior of this contact form by adding code snippets.'=>'<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customise the behaviour of this contact form by adding code snippets.','In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank.'=>'In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank.','<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similar to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully.'=>'<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similarly to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully.','<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here.'=>'<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here.','<strong>Form</strong> is a content of HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here.'=>'<strong>Form</strong> is a content of an HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here.','<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labeling a contact form, and can be edited.'=>'<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labelling a contact form, and can be edited.','On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:'=>'On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:','<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID.'=>'<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID.','<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title.'=>'<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title.','Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:'=>'Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:','On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target.'=>'On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target.','Mail-tags'=>'Mail-tags','Form-tags'=>'Form-tags','Available Actions'=>'Available Actions','Overview'=>'Overview','https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/'=>'https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/','File attachments'=>'File attachments','Use HTML content type'=>'Use HTML content type','Message body'=>'Message body','Additional headers'=>'Additional headers','Subject'=>'Subject','From'=>'From','To'=>'To','In the following fields, you can use these mail-tags:'=>'In the following fields, you can use these mail-tags:','Mail (2) is an additional mail template often used as an autoresponder.'=>'Mail (2) is an additional mail template often used as an autoresponder.','Use Mail (2)'=>'Use Mail (2)','Mail (2)'=>'Mail (2)','Y/m/d'=>'y/m/d','Edit &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'Edit &#8220;%s&#8221;','Edit'=>'Edit','Date'=>'Date','Author'=>'Author','Shortcode'=>'Shortcode','Title'=>'Title','Additional Settings'=>'Additional Settings','Additional Settings (%d)'=>'Additional Set